This package provides Python libNeuroML, for working with neuronal models
specified in NeuroML (http://neuroml.org)

Documentation is available at http://readthedocs.org/docs/libneuroml/en/latest/

The project home page is at http://neuroml.org/neuroml2 (this needs to be updated to point to Github...)

For installation instructions, see doc/install.txt

